## About MINING WORLD RUSSIA

MINING WORLD RUSSIA is the 30th International Exhibition for Mining, Mineral Processing, Mining Machinery and Equipment. As Russia's premier mining industry event, it attracts global equipment manufacturers and Russian mining operators.

## Exhibition Sectors

Mining Machinery | Mineral Processing | Exploration Technology | Safety Equipment | Automation & Control | Mining Services

## Event Highlights

**400+ Exhibitors** and **15,000+ Visitors** make MINING WORLD RUSSIA the key platform for accessing Russia's vast mining industry and mineral resources sector.

## Why Attend

Access the Russian mining market, discover latest mining technologies, connect with mining companies and equipment suppliers, and explore opportunities in one of the world's largest mineral resource markets.
